    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated mushrooms </strong>and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1626718159299-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
