          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1626718159299-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, dissolve your<strong> tomato paste</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p><p>Grate your<strong> cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and<strong> white wine vinegar</strong> in a small bowl and set aside for later – this is your <strong>zingy mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1626718165248-x200.jpg",
