            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1626718169384-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and add them to a tray, cut-side up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until warmed through and slightly crispy</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then remove 2 <strong>outer leaves </strong>per person (save these for your burger!) and shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626718185711-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626718185711-x400.jpg",
