          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626718221249-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626718221249-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626718221249-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626718221249-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed ciabatta </strong>with the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong>, <strong>Mexican-style pulled mushrooms </strong>and <strong>zingy mayo</strong> – these are your<strong> Mexican-style pulled mushroom burgers</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> Mexican-style pulled mushroom burger </strong>with the<strong> paprika fries</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> diced tomato </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle any<strong> remaining zingy mayo </strong>over the<strong> </strong>lettuce and tomato</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
